      "message": "v5.13: 3/7 cluster resolution - 11 institutions, +10 net roles\n\nEnrichment v5.13 focused on resolving the 3/7 cluster (11 institutions\nsitting at exactly 3/7 coverage, 44 roles recoverable).\n\nKey achievements:\n- 11 NEW role additions across 6 institutions (all MEDIUM-HIGH to MEDIUM confidence):\n  * SMBC MY CFO: Norihiro Oyanagi (conf 90, official Annual Financial Statement 31 Mar 2025)\n  * PBSNB Head of GRC: Wong Ching Fai @ Christopher (conf 90, official pbsn.com.my)\n  * JCorp Head of Compliance: Mohd Azmi Hitam (Chief Governance Officer, conf 80)\n  * PNSB CRO: Mohammed Hanafi Bin Muhi (Senior Manager Integriti, conf 80)\n  * PNSB Head of Compliance: Mohammed Hanafi Bin Muhi (conf 75)\n  * JCorp Head of Internal Audit: Mohd Nordin Jamaludin (Chief Corporate Services Officer, conf 70)\n  * Setel Head of Compliance + Head of GRC: Fazni Ismail (General Counsel, conf 65/60)\n  * Wise Head of GRC: Jessica Winter (Chief Legal Officer, conf 65)\n- 1 CORRECTION: SMBC MY CISO - previous entry was CEO Atsuhide Shiojiri\n  misfiled as CISO. Replaced with NOT FOUND audit trail (conf 35).\n- 31 NOT FOUND audit trail entries documented across 10 institutions\n  (replacing empty cells with sourced negative findings).\n\nCoverage statistics:\n- Total roles filled: 774/1442 = 53.7% (+0.7% from v5.12)\n- 5/7 institutions: 27 -> 31 (+4)\n- 4/7 institutions: 8 -> 10 (+2)\n- 3/7 institutions: 11 -> 5 (-6, cluster resolved)\n\n3/7 cluster promotions:\n- 3/7 -> 5/7: JCorp, Setel (both rows), PNSB\n- 3/7 -> 4/7: PBSNB, Wise\n\nRemaining 3/7 (5 institutions, all roles confirmed NOT FOUND with audit):\nAmMetLife, MSIG Insurance, Deutsche Bank MY, Maybank IB, SMBC MY\n\nClassification: TLP:AMBER",
